  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个风险响应流程，核心是从DiagnosticEngine出发，先经过LabAnalyzer做风险分级判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那LabAnalyzer是一个判断节点对吧？我需要用菱形来表示。分级的话，具体分几档？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分三档：高风险、中高风险、中低风险。高风险和中高风险都要回到DiagnosticEngine做深度诊断，中低风险直接走EMR同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：DiagnosticEngine指向LabAnalyzer，然后LabAnalyzer分出三条带标签的线——高、中高、中/低。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，高风险那条线标\"高\"，中高那条标\"中高\"，第三条标\"中/低\"，注意用斜杠。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已标注。现在高风险和中高风险都指回DiagnosticEngine，中/低那条指向EMR_Sync。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。但这里有个细节：高风险和中高风险经过DiagnosticEngine处理后，还需要再走一次EMR同步。另外中低风险那条也要汇总到同一个EMR节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以EMR_Sync是一个汇聚点？三条路径最终都要到达这里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，但流程是：高风险和中高风险先到DiagnosticEngine，再从DiagnosticEngine到EMR_Sync；中低风险直接到EMR_Sync。三条线最终都汇入EMR_Sync。",
      "elements_involved": [
