    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我检查一下：DiagnosticEngine→LabAnalyzer→三分支→两条回DiagnosticEngine、一条直接到EMR_Sync→三条汇总到EMR_Sync→最后回到DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
