    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下。把中高风险那条线从指向EMR_Sync改为指向DiagnosticEngine，和高风险保持一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在对了。再确认一下汇聚逻辑：DiagnosticEngine处理完高风险和中高风险后，两条线都指向EMR_Sync，加上中低风险那条，三条线进EMR_Sync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整。现在结构是：LabAnalyzer三分支，高和中高都到DiagnosticEngine，中/低到EMR_Sync；然后DiagnosticEngine有两条线出来到EMR_Sync，加上直接那条，共三条入EMR_Sync；最后EMR_Sync回到DiagnosticEngine。",
